<p>An explosion and fire at a Waldo’s discount store in central Hermosillo, Sonora, on Saturday killed at least 23 people and left about a dozen others injured, officials said, in a tragedy that struck during Day of the Dead weekend . State authorities said most deaths were linked to toxic gas inhalation and that a faulty electric transformer located inside the building is the working focus of an investigation; investigators have ruled out an attack on civilians . Sonora’s governor ordered a transparent probe and praised the fast, professional emergency response, and Mexico’s president conveyed condolences and dispatched federal support teams for victims and families .</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/oGKyb6d_fzTtUEI5jzehb1Zqv8At6oHpY78jQGqM78K_vHZJic4yB4vzXjT0ftMJjeYmXEMhMDvFKD4RaBcFvIg78jmd2_iQcIVuDBQIVoiD' alt='The exterior of a Waldo’s store in Hermosillo is blackened after a fire killed at least 23 people.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Victim profile: Officials said a number of the dead were minors and that many fatalities stemmed from inhaling toxic gases rather than direct burns</li><li>Investigation focus: Prosecutors described the working assumption as an accidental blast and are examining a transformer inside the store as a potential cause</li><li>Emergency response: Firefighters and health teams controlled the blaze, treated survivors at Hermosillo hospitals, and local officials publicly commended their professionalism</li><li>Damage visible: Images and video published by local media show the store’s façade blackened, shattered windows and firefighters battling intense flames at the scene</li></ul><blockquote>Sadly, a number of the victims we’ve found were minors - Alfonso Durazo</blockquote><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Alfonso Durazo, governor of Sonora: I have ordered an extensive and transparent investigation to determine the causes of the incident and figure out those responsible; emergency, security and health services responded with great professionalism and commitment. (<a href='https://www.dawn.com/news/1952726/supermarket-explosion-kills-at-least-23-in-mexico'>Dawn</a>)</li><li>Prosecutor&#x27;s office (Sonora): The working assumption is that the incident was accidental; the investigation is looking into a transformer located inside the store. (<a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2025/11/2/at-least-23-killed-in-supermarket-explosion-in-mexicos-sonora-state'>Al Jazeera</a>)</li><li>President Claudia Sheinbaum: I have been in contact with the Sonora governor to provide support where needed and I&#x27;ve instructed the interior secretary to send a support team to assist the families and the injured. (<a href='https://www.thehindu.com/news/international/fire-at-waldo-department-store-explosion-mexico-hermosillo/article70231928.ece'>The Hindu</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/fire-explosion-store-northwestern-mexico-leave-23-dead-127103081'>Fire and explosion at store in Mexico leave at least 23 dead and a dozen injured</a> - abcnews.go.com</li><li><a href='https://www.dw.com/en/mexico-fire-at-general-store-kills-23-people/a-74588595'>Mexico: Fire at general store kills 23 people</a> - dw.com</li><li><a href='https://www.scmp.com/news/world/americas/article/3331209/children-among-23-killed-mexico-store-fire-festive-weekend-turns-tragic'>Mexico store fire kills 23 as festive weekend turns tragic</a> - scmp.com</li><li><a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2025/11/2/at-least-23-killed-in-supermarket-explosion-in-mexicos-sonora-state'>At least 23 killed in supermarket blast in Mexico’s Sonora state</a> - aljazeera.com</li><li><a href='https://www.nytimes.com/2025/11/01/world/americas/mexico-fire-hermosillo-sonora.html'>Fire in Hermosillo, Mexico, Kills at Least 23 at Waldo’s Store</a> - nytimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.dawn.com/news/1952726/supermarket-explosion-kills-at-least-23-in-mexico'>Supermarket explosion kills at least 